title: Star Wars - The Clone Wars Legacy (The Clone Wars Unaired)
description:
Star Wars - The Clone Wars Unaired Episodes

This is a collection of 8 episodes that didn't get finished in time for the 6th and final season of The Clone Wars. The only part of these episodes that did get finished was the voice acting. If you can't deal with bad animation you shouldn't waste your time with this.
This is for all The Clone Wars fans that got cheated out of one of the highest ranking shows (anywhere from #1 to #7 depending on who you ask) when Disney bought the series and ended it without explanation.


The Clone Wars Legacy
